00:02:23.578 --> 00:02:24.567
trying to answer?

00:02:24.567 --> 00:02:26.014
Well, at least the was it's written,

00:02:26.014 --> 00:02:27.721
it seems like she's trying to answer

00:02:27.721 --> 00:02:29.543
whether or not her antibiotic works,

00:02:29.543 --> 00:02:31.112
whether it's an effective antibiotic,

00:02:31.112 --> 00:02:33.517
whether it's capable of killing bacteria.

00:02:34.424 --> 00:02:35.837
You might be tempted to
say, "Okay, well look.

00:02:35.837 --> 00:02:37.108
