00:03:06.651 --> 00:03:08.750
and it somehow it just spontaneously

00:03:08.750 --> 00:03:09.784
died on its own.

00:03:10.322 --> 00:03:12.129
She can't say with confidence that it

00:03:12.129 --> 00:03:13.864
was definitely ... it was definitely

00:03:13.864 --> 00:03:15.101
