00:03:20.734 --> 00:03:22.640
She would have to have a control and

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:23.555
a treatment group,

00:03:23.555 --> 00:03:25.980
where everything is equal except for the

00:03:25.980 --> 00:03:27.423
