00:03:40.394 --> 00:03:42.678
except for the treatment group,

00:03:42.678 --> 00:03:45.562
has the antibiotic applied to it.

00:03:45.562 --> 00:03:48.429
Then she saw that in the treatment group

00:03:48.675 --> 00:03:51.037
